item.description:
@justa_lol wrote:

if you have jdk-6u4 use this
@echo off
“C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_04\bin\javac.exe” *.java
pause

if you have jdk-6u3 use this
@echo off
“C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_03\bin\javac.exe” *.java
pause

if you have jdk-6u2 use this
